{"tid":1467932,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"獨立監測示威者投訴科 正式成立","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:44:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:53:39.000Z","uid":158283,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"886be98fc70ebc05952c29b9d0125a052ddc984a","tid":1467932,"uid":158283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:44:06.000Z","msg":"我地會接收市民對示威者既投訴<br />\n投訴人士必須提供完整 示威者名稱 及 身份證號碼 先會受理<br />\n以免有支那人混入影響其他案件審理速度<br />\n<br />\n投訴人士必須詳細客觀陳述事件，不得加以任何個人感情或批判<br />\n以免影響本會深入調查及影響委員裁決，對被調查人士造成不公<br />\n<br />\n本會所作出一切裁決皆無約束力，示威者亦可以當笑話聽<br />\n預計示威者接納意見率會遠超監警會<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1bf76004de288aeb30580bc6b8fab1bbfce2383","tid":1467932,"uid":158283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:46:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d429496547de5477129fc129c8608ea0cd1905e3","tid":1467932,"uid":77137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:47:20.000Z","msg":"玩膠文<br />\n不推文回覆"},{"pid":"e025d583806e35b63add6409e659596cd42e576f","tid":1467932,"uid":158283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d429496547de5477129fc129c8608ea0cd1905e3","tid":1467932,"uid":77137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:47:20.000Z","msg":"玩膠文<br />\n不推文回覆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:53:39.000Z","msg":"唔係玩膠<br />\n係大家無權利決定香港人想做既事<br />\n可以檢討唔可以控制 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}